Browser front-end for the Reliability Engine. The engine in src/engine/ is the same logic
as the OpenClaw plugin (github.com/Laninthalesdran/openclaw-reliability-engine), packaged
for the browser. Cross-browser builds via WXT (wxt.dev); cross-browser `browser` API via
webextension-polyfill. Leading-language detector grounded in published research — see
src/data/leading_language.json citations.
